WEBVTT

19:23.000 --> 19:25.870 line:80%
When I was young,
I read a fragment of a Go manual

19:26.350 --> 19:27.880 line:80%
called "The Mystery of Qi."

19:28.110 --> 19:30.760 line:80%
I heard that your Library
has over 10,000 books.

19:30.760 --> 19:32.000 line:80%
I wanted to find it,

19:32.520 --> 19:34.180 line:80%
but I haven't been able to yet.
